55Z","title":"Reasoning hook triggered without tool action","type":"other"},"type":"compressed"},"obs_mr9tfce3_06d05593fdd5":{"observation":{"concepts":["LLM provider fallback chain","reasoning fallback for null content","dual server architecture","Vercel serverless environment variables"],"confidence":1,"facts":["User input \"Вўцвіў ЖхГвѓ┤ВдЮВІю Вќ┤вќеЖ▒░ Ж░ЎВЋё?\" returned fallback error: \"ВБёВєАьЋЕвІѕвІц. ьўёВъг AI Вёюв╣ёВіцВЌљ ВЮ╝ВІюВаЂВЮИ вгИВаюЖ░ђ ВъѕВіхвІѕвІц.\"","Repeated input \"вІцВІюьЋ┤\" produced same error","ZAI GLM-5: \"Weekly/Monthly Limit Exhausted\" (resets 2026-07-08 08:29:53)","OpenCode GLM-5.2: \"Missing API key\" (OPENCODE_KEY env var not set)","Nous stepfun/step-3.7-flash:free: returned content: null + reasoning only","Nous openai/gpt-oss-120b:free: 404 Model not found","Nous nex-agi/nex-n2-pro:free: 404 Model not found","OpenRouter: \"No cookie auth credentials found\" (OPENROUTER_KEY not set)","Fix applied: api/index.py:chat_from_nous() now uses msg.get(\"reasoning\") fallback when content is null; max_tokens increased 1500Рєњ2500","Remaining: remove duplicate OpenCode call at lines 2407-2411 (duplicates 2372-2375); apply same reasoning fallback to server.py"],"files":["/home/rg3270/.local/share/mimocode/memory/sessions/ses_0c662c7c3ffe67rW13w0xXA3Xf/checkpoint.md","api/index.py","server.py","app.js","vercel.json"],"id":"obs_mr9tfce3_06d05593fdd5","importance":8,"narrative":"The dashboard chat AI fails because all configured LLM providers return errors in sequence. The Nous free model only returns reasoning without content, so a fallback was added in api/index.py:chat_from_nous(). Remaining work includes removing a duplicate OpenCode call in the retry chain, setting missing environment variables (OPENCODE_KEY, OPENROUTER_KEY), and applying the same reasoning fallback to server.py per the dual-server rule.","sessionId":"ses_0c65df97bffenBxPcEzKn5wcXp","subtitle":"Reading session checkpoint for imooc dashboard chat AI issue","timestamp":"2026-07-06T22:52:33.524Z","title":"Dashboard chat AI debugging: all LLM providers failing","type":"file_read"},"type":"compressed"},"obs_mr9tfcmg_6e0558a9aef2":{"observation":{"concepts":["project_memory","dual_server_architecture","llm_fallback_chain","lightweight_charts","korean_stock_market","vercel_serverless","server_side_news_filtering","kst_market_hours"],"confidence":1,"facts":["Project: Korean stock market dashboard (`stock-dashboard`) showing real-time quotes, news, AI analysis, and candlestick charts for KRX stocks","Deployment: Vercel at `stock-dashboard-wine-gamma.vercel.app`, GitHub repo `jmpark333/stockm` main branch","LLM fallback chain: ZAI (glm-5) Рєњ NOUS (stepfun/step-3.7-flash:free) Рєњ OpenRouter (nex-n2-pro:free Рєњ gpt-oss-120b:free)","Dual server architecture: `server.py` local (port 8090) and `api/index.py` Vercel Flask must mirror endpoints exactly","Market hours: KST 09:00-15:30 only for ВъЦВцЉ/ВъЦвДѕЖ░љ/ВъЦВаё determination","Frontend index display: в│ђвЈЎвЦа (%) only; no combined в│ђвЈЎЖ░њ + в│ђвЈЎвЦа to avoid line breaks","Chatbot uses server cache data; search functionality disabled","Stock fee/tax deduction: вДцвЈёЖИѕВЋА ├Ќ 0.215% (ВѕўВѕўвБї 0.015% + ВаюВёИЖИѕ 0.20%); fields sellFee, realizedProfit, realizedProfitRate","Charts: lightweight-charts@4.1.3 with Naver Finance `siseJson.naver` API (parse with ast.literal_eval for Python list syntax)","System prompt: must minimize tokens (previously reduced from 242 lines to 6 core rules)","Рќ▓Рќ╝ вХђьўИ system for variation display; LLM must not confuse signs","Conversation context: only role == \"assistant\" items passed to AI to prevent question repetition bug","Approval required before any code modification or new task"],"files":["/home/rg3270/.local/share/mimocode/memory/projects/c7d56d4e-4055-47be-ae32-d050be5aa949/MEMORY.md"],"id":"obs_mr9tfcmg_6e0558a9aef2","importance":8,"narrative":"Read the project memory file containing durable rules and architectural decisions for the Korean stock market dashboard. These rules enforce consistent behavior across both local and Vercel server environments, including LLM provider fallback order, market hour logic, stock fee calculations, and chart implementation. All future sessions must adhere to these constraints and mirror changes between server.py and api/index.py.","sessionId":"ses_0c65df97bffenBxPcEzKn5wcXp","subtitle":"Durable project memory with architectural constraints and operational rules","timestamp":"2026-07-06T22:52:33.825Z","title":"MEMORY.md - Korean stock dashboard project rules","type":"file_read"},"type":"compressed"},"obs_mr9tfcy5_4346e2d6b334":{"observation":{"concepts":["LLM provider fallback","API key management","rate limiting","model 404 errors","call_llm"],"confidence":1,"facts":["Chat AI returned fallback message: \"ВБёВєАьЋЕвІѕвІц. ьўёВъг AI Вёюв╣ёВіцВЌљ ВЮ╝ВІюВаЂВЮИ вгИВаюЖ░ђ ВъѕВіхвІѕвІц\"","call_llm() fallback triggered because all LLM providers failed","api/index.py contains hardcoded ZAI_KEY; server.py uses environment variables","OPENCODE_KEY and OPENROUTER_KEY are unset, causing providers to be skipped","Direct API tests: ZAI rate limited (7/8 reset), OpenCode key missing, Nous stepfun returns null content with reasoning only, Nous openai/nex models return 404, OpenRouter key missing","api/index.py:chat_from_nous() was modified to add reasoning fallback","server.py needs same reasoning fallback modification plus removal of duplicate OpenCode call in call_llm"],"files":["/home/rg3270/.local/share/mimocode/memory/sessions/ses_0c662c7c3ffe67rW13w0xXA3Xf/notes.md"],"id":"obs_mr9tfcy5_4346e2d6b334","importance":6,"narrative":"Session notes document active debugging of a chat service where all LLM providers are failing, triggering a generic service error message. The agent identified multiple provider issues through direct API testing: rate limiting, missing API keys, null content responses, and 404 errors. Applied a reasoning fallback patch to chat_from_nous() in api/index.py, with pending similar changes needed in server.py.","sessionId":"ses_0c65df97bffenBxPcEzKn5wcXp","subtitle":"Troubleshooting chat service fallback behavior","timestamp":"2026-07-06T22:52:34.248Z","title":"Session notes: LLM provider failures investigation","type":"file_read"},"type":"compressed"},"obs_mr9tfd9a_ee42ce399c9a":{"observation":{"concepts":["hook event","step completion"],"confidence":0.9,"facts":["Hook type: step_finish","Timestamp: 2026-07-06T22:52:34.650Z"],"files":[],"id":"obs_mr9tfd9a_ee42ce399c9a","importance":2,"narrative":"A step_finish hook event was triggered, indicating completion of a workflow step at the specified timestamp. No additional context about which step was completed or its outcome is provided.","sessionId":"ses_0c65df97bffenBxPcEzKn5wcXp","subtitle":"Completion notification with timestamp 2026-07-06T22:52:34.650Z","timestamp":"2026-07-06T22:52:34.650Z","title":"Step finish hook event","type":"notification"},"type":"compressed"},"obs_mr9tfdbq_dbbff2d68946":{"observation":{"concepts":["patch application","system hook","code deployment"],"confidence":1,"facts":["Patch application completed without errors","Timestamp: 2026-07-06T22:52:34.738Z","No specific file changes or patch details provided"],"files":["unknown"],"id":"obs_mr9tfdbq_dbbff2d68946","importance":5,"narrative":"A patch_applied hook fired successfully at the specified timestamp, indicating code changes were applied to the repository. However, no details about the patch content, modified files, or changes are included in the hook payload.","sessionId":"ses_0c65df97bffenBxPcEzKn5wcXp","subtitle":"System hook notification indicating patch was applied","timestamp":"2026-07-06T22:52:34.738Z","title":"Patch applied successfully","type":"notification"},"type":"compressed"},"obs_mr9tfijb_e6148bd837dc":{"observation":{"concepts":["task management tool","input validation","type checking"],"confidence":1,"facts":["Tool: task","Operation parameter value: \"list\" (string)","Expected type: object","Error code: invalid_type","Path: [\"operation\"]"],"files":[],"id":"obs_mr9tfijb_e6148bd837dc","importance":2,"narrative":"The task tool was invoked with a string value for the operation parameter instead of an object. The tool's schema requires an object at that location, but a string was provided, causing the input validation to fail.","sessionId":"ses_0c65df97bffenBxPcEzKn5wcXp","subtitle":"Operation parameter expected object, received string","timestamp":"2026-07-06T22:52:41.490Z","title":"Task tool called with invalid arguments","type":"error"},"type":"compressed"},"obs_mr9tfmc9_f52e45606ff9":{"observation":{"concepts":["task management"],"confidence":1,"facts":["Task list operation completed successfully","Result set is empty","Timestamp: 2026-07-06T22:52:46.421Z"],"files":[],"id":"obs_mr9tfmc9_f52e45606ff9","importance":1,"narrative":"A task list command was executed to enumerate available tasks. The system returned no results, indicating there are no pending or active tasks currently registered.","sessionId":"ses_0c65df97bffenBxPcEzKn5wcXp","subtitle":"No pending or existing tasks found in system","timestamp":"2026-07-06T22:52:46.421Z","title":"Task list returned empty","type":"task"},"type":"compressed"},"obs_mr9tg26h_a7704c3cd250":{"observation":{"concepts":["Nous reasoning fallback","duplicate API call removal","max_tokens threshold","Vercel serverless deployment","dual server architecture"],"confidence":1,"facts":["Modified `api/index.py`: chat_from_nous() reasoning fallback (2301-2332) when content is null, max_tokens 1500Рєњ2500, removed duplicate OpenCode call in call_llm() (2370-2425)","Modified `server.py`: chat_from_nous() reasoning fallback (2095-2126)","Verification: stepfun/step-3.7-flash:free returns reasoning (1601 chars) + content (501 chars) with max_tokens=8000, finish_reason=stop","ZAI API limit exceeded, resets 2026-07-08 08:29:53 KST","Git repo: stock-dashboard (jmpark333/stockm main), Vercel: stock-dashboard.vercel.app, local: port 8090"],"files":["api/index.py","server.py","vercel.json","app.js"],"id":"obs_mr9tg26h_a7704c3cd250","importance":8,"narrative":"User reported dashboard chat AI failing with a service error after asking about Korean stock market forecasts. Applied fixes to both Vercel and local servers: added reasoning fallback for null content, removed duplicate OpenCode call, and increased max_tokens. Verification confirmed the model now returns both reasoning and content with increased token limit.","sessionId":"ses_0c65df97bffenBxPcEzKn5wcXp","subtitle":"Fixed Nous API response failures across Vercel and local servers with reasoning fallback, duplicate OpenCode call removal, and max_tokens increase","timestamp":"2026-07-06T22:53:06.950Z","title":"Dashboard chat AI fix: reasoning fallback + duplicate removal","type":"file_write"},"type":"compressed"},"obs_mr9tgvnp_7e1fd5bbc8f6":{"observation":{"concepts":["Korean stock market dashboard","dual server architecture","LLM fallback chain","lightweight-charts candlestick","system prompt optimization"],"confidence":1,"facts":["LLM priority chain: ZAI (glm-5) Рєњ NOUS Рєњ OPENROUTER via call_llm()","User approval mandatory for any code modifications","Stock predictions forbidden; use only provided data without speculative language","Sell fee structure: 0.215% total (0.015% commission + 0.20% tax); fields: sellFee, realizedProfit, realizedProfitRate","Conversation history filter: include only role == \"assistant\" messages to prevent AI repetition bug","System prompt reduced to 6 core rules on 2026-06-30 to minimize LLM response time","Dual server: server.py (local:8090) and api/index.py (Vercel) must receive identical changes","Chart library: lightweight-charts@4.1.3 + Naver Finance siseJson.naver API (returns Python list syntax)","Production: stock-dashboard-wine-gamma.vercel.app from jmpark333/stockm main branch","Frontend index display: show only change rate (%), not absolute value, to prevent line wrapping"],"files":["/home/rg3270/.local/share/mimocode/memory/projects/c7d56d4e-4055-47be-ae32-d050be5aa949/MEMORY.md"],"id":"obs_mr9tgvnp_7e1fd5bbc8f6","importance":9,"narrative":"Updated the project's durable MEMORY.md with hard constraints, architectural decisions, and operational rules for the Korean stock market dashboard. The document specifies the LLM fallback order, KST market-hour logic, dual-server synchronization requirements, and precise UI formatting rules that all sessions must respect.","sessionId":"ses_0c65df97bffenBxPcEzKn5wcXp","subtitle":"Writing durable Korean stock market dashboard knowledge to project MEMORY.md","timestamp":"2026-07-06T22:53:45.154Z","title":"Project memory updated with stock dashboard rules","type":"file_write"},"type":"compressed"},"obs_mr9tgwbg_6bcb34a54f89":{"observation":{"concepts":["session scratchpad","checkpoint reconciliation","duplicate detection"],"confidence":1,"facts":["File path: /home/rg3270/.local/share/mimocode/memory/sessions/ses_0c662c7c3ffe67rW13w0xXA3Xf/notes.md","Entry format: `## [turn N ┬и YYYY-MM-DDTHH:MM:SSZ]` with minute precision UTC","Checkpoint writer reconciles entries at checkpoint events","Duplicate content rule: add `(see entry above)` reference instead of duplicating"],"files":["/home/rg3270/.local/share/mimocode/memory/sessions/ses_0c662c7c3ffe67rW13w0xXA3Xf/notes.md"],"id":"obs_mr9tgwbg_6bcb34a54f89","importance":2,"narrative":"Created a new notes.md scratchpad file with formatting instructions for the agent to record session observations. The file defines how to timestamp entries, avoid duplication, and how a checkpoint writer will reconcile the buffer at checkpoint events.","sessionId":"ses_0c65df97bffenBxPcEzKn5wcXp","subtitle":"Initialize free-form notes buffer for main agent","timestamp":"2026-07-06T22:53:46.008Z","title":"Create session scratchpad notes file","type":"file_write"},"type":"compressed"}}␀Џ␀$║  